1
00:00:44,362 --> 00:00:49,137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

2
00:00:49,650 --> 00:00:52,200
=Episode 19=

3
00:00:53,479 --> 00:00:54,880
It's not aconitine poisoning?

4
00:00:55,079 --> 00:00:56,039
It's scopolamine

5
00:00:56,439 --> 00:00:58,039
extracted from datura.

6
00:00:58,520 --> 00:01:00,359
The entire datura plant is highly toxic.

7
00:01:00,612 --> 00:01:01,679
Scopolamine

8
00:01:01,679 --> 00:01:02,799
can also cause fainting.

9
00:01:02,987 --> 00:01:04,267
And its symptoms

10
00:01:04,267 --> 00:01:05,812
closely resemble aconitine poisoning.

11
00:01:06,039 --> 00:01:08,320
Aconite poisoning
blocks peripheral circulation

12
00:01:08,600 --> 00:01:10,519
and causes cardiac arrhythmia.

13
00:01:10,519 --> 00:01:12,719
Datura poisoning
suppresses the sweat glands

14
00:01:12,719 --> 00:01:14,439
and overstimulates
the sympathetic nerves.

15
00:01:14,870 --> 00:01:16,120
In traditional Chinese medicine,

16
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:18,439
both conditions
produce a deep and rapid pulse.

17
00:01:18,912 --> 00:01:21,400
But the two poisons
affect the pupils differently.

18
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:22,359
Wait, stop talking.

19
00:01:22,359 --> 00:01:23,830
Let me ask you.
Are you a medical student?

20
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:24,480
Do you even know anything?

21
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:25,159
Hold on.

22
00:01:26,079 --> 00:01:28,159
This young man seems
to have quite a background.

23
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:29,280
Please, continue.

24
00:01:30,150 --> 00:01:32,000
With aconitine poisoning,
the pupils constrict.

25
00:01:32,175 --> 00:01:34,079
With datura poisoning,
the pupils dilate.

26
00:01:34,500 --> 00:01:35,550
But Aoxue's pupils

27
00:01:35,775 --> 00:01:37,245
are irregularly dilated,

28
00:01:37,375 --> 00:01:38,655
not the pin-point pupils

29
00:01:38,655 --> 00:01:40,000
seen with aconitine poisoning.

30
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:42,959
Did you...

31
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:45,040
notice this from the beginning?

32
00:01:45,599 --> 00:01:46,200
That's right.

33
00:01:46,775 --> 00:01:47,895
Because I already know

34
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:49,879
how Aoxue was poisoned.

35
00:01:50,580 --> 00:01:52,990
She has a habit of lighting incense
when she practices martial arts.

36
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,778
Someone hid the poison
in the incense sticks.

37
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:55,958
Over time,

38
00:01:56,719 --> 00:01:58,560
the toxin accumulated in her body.

39
00:01:59,237 --> 00:02:00,159
That training room

40
00:02:00,159 --> 00:02:01,519
is usually used only by her,

41
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:03,190
so none of the rest
of you were affected.

42
00:02:03,790 --> 00:02:04,560
No need to doubt it.

43
00:02:05,587 --> 00:02:06,719
I already had it tested.

44
00:02:12,450 --> 00:02:16,175
(Incense Stick - Test Report)

45
00:02:16,250 --> 00:02:17,812
(Test Result)

46
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:19,100
Have it investigated.

47
00:02:19,879 --> 00:02:21,120
Find out who tampered with it.

48
00:02:21,479 --> 00:02:21,840
Go.

49
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:22,280
Yes.

50
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:25,840
Dr. Shi,

51
00:02:26,479 --> 00:02:27,840
how do we cure datura poisoning?

52
00:02:28,180 --> 00:02:30,110
According to Emergency Prescriptions
Kept Up One's Sleeve,

53
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:32,639
mix aged vinegar
with mirabilite and administer it.

54
00:02:33,439 --> 00:02:34,439
Then add magnetite powder

55
00:02:34,639 --> 00:02:36,759
to purge the remaining toxins

56
00:02:37,039 --> 00:02:38,000
downward.

57
00:02:38,425 --> 00:02:40,471
This comes from the Compendium
of Materia Medica.

58
00:02:40,637 --> 00:02:43,000
Then combine it
with Seven-Star Lamp Moxibustion,

59
00:02:43,060 --> 00:02:45,162
burning moxa on key points
along the Governor Vessel,

60
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:47,537
using the heat
to draw the toxin outward.

61
00:02:47,879 --> 00:02:49,159
And this method comes from...

62
00:02:50,262 --> 00:02:51,599
From my master's notes.

63
00:02:52,199 --> 00:02:53,759
The same old man I mentioned earlier.

64
00:02:54,137 --> 00:02:55,925
May I ask...

65
00:02:56,237 --> 00:02:58,080
What is his name?

66
00:02:58,319 --> 00:02:59,039
Quan Baohua.

67
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,400
Could you repeat that?

68
00:03:03,479 --> 00:03:04,360
Quan Baohua.

69
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,280
Martial Uncle!

70
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,960
Please allow me to pay my respects.

71
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,680
No, that won't do!

72
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,400
What "Martial Uncle"?

73
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:16,520
Well...

74
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:18,479
When my master was young,

75
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:20,800
he once received guidance

76
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:21,550
from your master.

77
00:03:21,719 --> 00:03:22,680
By seniority,

78
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,520
that makes you

79
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:25,360
my martial uncle.

80
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,560
When Master Quan was young,

81
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:29,080
he was a renowned master

82
00:03:29,319 --> 00:03:31,120
throughout the medical world.

83
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:32,390
But later on,

84
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:34,360
no one knows why he suddenly went
into seclusion.

85
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,240
Like a divine dragon,

86
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,900
you glimpse the head,
but never the tail.

87
00:03:39,080 --> 00:03:39,879
Mr. Qin,

88
00:03:40,719 --> 00:03:42,479
to be honest,

89
00:03:42,775 --> 00:03:44,764
when I managed
to wake your daughter that day,

90
00:03:44,879 --> 00:03:48,562
it was entirely thanks
to him secretly lending me his strength.

91
00:03:48,837 --> 00:03:51,062
Otherwise, with just my 50 years of...

92
00:03:52,820 --> 00:03:54,790
That's enough.
We shouldn't speak of this anymore.

93
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:56,719
Martial Uncle...

94
00:03:57,719 --> 00:03:59,240
I...

95
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:01,479
I gained fame too early.

96
00:04:02,319 --> 00:04:03,680
I became arrogant and vain,

97
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:04,680
showing off everywhere.

98
00:04:05,039 --> 00:04:06,280
Only now do I realize

99
00:04:06,639 --> 00:04:08,400
there are always

100
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,719
greater masters beyond.

101
00:04:10,199 --> 00:04:11,759
I'm deeply ashamed.

102
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,319
Dr. Shi,

103
00:04:13,319 --> 00:04:14,280
please don't say that.

104
00:04:14,987 --> 00:04:16,419
You're a miracle doctor too.

105
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:20,680
Ye Chen...

106
00:04:22,519 --> 00:04:23,160
Thank you.

107
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:26,160
As long as Aoxue is saved,
that's all that matters.

108
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,920
(It has the fragrance of rice
and osmanthus.)

109
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:34,560
(It's especially delicious.)

110
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:36,360
(The ingredients
and method are very simple.)

111
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:38,360
(Pour 75 grams of glutinous rice flour)

112
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,959
(and 225 grams
of rice flour into a bowl.)

113
00:04:39,959 --> 00:04:40,959
(Mix them evenly.)

114
00:04:40,959 --> 00:04:42,639
(Prepare 105 grams of warm water,)

115
00:04:42,639 --> 00:04:45,319
(add 50 grams of sugar,
and stir until the sugar dissolves.)

116
00:04:45,319 --> 00:04:46,759
(Cut the dough into shapes you like.)

117
00:04:46,759 --> 00:04:47,839
(Then cover it with a layer...)

118
00:04:47,839 --> 00:04:50,079
What's this? You're cooking today?

119
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:51,439
Where's Ye Chen?

120
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,319
Mom,

121
00:04:52,319 --> 00:04:53,240
Ye Chen is busy.

122
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,319
Let's not disturb him.

123
00:04:54,439 --> 00:04:54,959
I...

124
00:04:55,079 --> 00:04:56,199
I had nothing to do,

125
00:04:56,199 --> 00:04:57,199
so I made this for fun.

126
00:04:57,199 --> 00:04:58,190
You go ahead with your work.

127
00:05:00,439 --> 00:05:01,360
That Ye Chen...

128
00:05:01,639 --> 00:05:02,240
Honestly.

129
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:06,131
(If you want osmanthus cake,
you can just make it at home.)

130
00:05:14,210 --> 00:05:15,900
Grab a bite
before you continue studying.

131
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:17,319
I'll be done soon.

132
00:05:22,575 --> 00:05:23,379
Osmanthus cake?

133
00:05:24,620 --> 00:05:25,839
I just learned how to make it.

134
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,639
I'm not sure if it'll taste good.

135
00:05:27,700 --> 00:05:31,062
♪If dreams are truly out of reach♪

136
00:05:31,700 --> 00:05:35,140
♪How did I end up meeting you?♪

137
00:05:35,439 --> 00:05:36,240
You fool.

138
00:05:37,639 --> 00:05:38,720
You made this yourself?

139
00:05:38,762 --> 00:05:40,825
♪If everything is destined♪

140
00:05:40,879 --> 00:05:43,480
I merely followed an online recipe.

141
00:05:43,959 --> 00:05:44,519
Try it.

142
00:05:47,550 --> 00:05:52,340
♪No matter how far away you are♪

143
00:05:53,279 --> 00:05:53,759
So?

144
00:05:58,199 --> 00:05:59,519
Is it that bad?

145
00:06:00,020 --> 00:06:02,439
That recipe online didn't really say how
to control the heat.

146
00:06:02,439 --> 00:06:04,050
Did I mess up the timing?

147
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:05,720
Churan...

148
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:08,480
Thank you.

149
00:06:09,631 --> 00:06:12,625
I thought I'd never again get to eat
osmanthus cake made by someone's hands.

150
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:15,275
If you

151
00:06:15,337 --> 00:06:16,498
don't mind that it tastes bad,

152
00:06:16,498 --> 00:06:17,890
I'll make it for you
every day from now on.

153
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:20,399
Let me try.

154
00:06:21,162 --> 00:06:23,675
♪A light always shines♪

155
00:06:23,975 --> 00:06:27,000
♪You're the direction in my heart♪

156
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:28,040
It's so sweet.

157
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:29,560
I must've added too much sugar.

158
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:30,680
Now it's turned bitter.

159
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:31,600
It's fine.

160
00:06:32,875 --> 00:06:33,755
I like bitter things.

161
00:06:33,825 --> 00:06:35,525
♪Riding the wind and breaking the waves♪

162
00:06:35,650 --> 00:06:39,512
♪Setting sail across the vast sea♪

163
00:06:40,279 --> 00:06:40,920
From now on,

164
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:43,399
I'll be with you through the sweet times,

165
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:44,360
and the bitter ones too.

166
00:06:44,912 --> 00:06:49,025
♪I will come to your side♪

167
00:06:49,387 --> 00:06:54,260
♪I'll brave thorns
and move forward without fear♪

168
00:06:54,550 --> 00:06:56,260
♪Riding the wind and breaking the waves♪

169
00:06:56,260 --> 00:07:00,420
♪Setting sail across the vast sea♪

170
00:07:00,420 --> 00:07:02,940
♪Before dawn♪

171
00:07:02,940 --> 00:07:05,500
♪When the flowers bloom♪

172
00:07:05,500 --> 00:07:10,060
♪I will come to your side♪

173
00:07:10,660 --> 00:07:13,340
♪Before dawn♪

174
00:07:13,340 --> 00:07:15,180
♪When the flowers bloom♪

175
00:07:15,399 --> 00:07:15,879
Dad...

176
00:07:15,962 --> 00:07:20,220
♪I will come to your side♪

177
00:07:21,975 --> 00:07:22,535
Aoxue.

178
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:26,199
Aoxue.

179
00:07:31,839 --> 00:07:32,920
You're awake!

180
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,000
It's okay now.

181
00:07:35,639 --> 00:07:36,240
You're okay.

182
00:07:36,380 --> 00:07:36,720
Yeah...

183
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:40,839
You're okay.

184
00:07:47,199 --> 00:07:48,160
Everything's fine now.

185
00:07:55,959 --> 00:07:56,639
You're okay.

186
00:08:04,839 --> 00:08:07,100
Dad, you're still thinking
about that incense burner?

187
00:08:07,879 --> 00:08:08,680
Not so loudly.

188
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:11,439
If your mom hears about it,
she'll start a fight with me again.

189
00:08:12,162 --> 00:08:14,590
If you really like it,
I'll find a way to get you another one.

190
00:08:15,010 --> 00:08:16,510
Don't go promising things like that.

191
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,200
I can't afford it.

192
00:08:19,399 --> 00:08:20,480
That Qian Hongyan

193
00:08:21,439 --> 00:08:23,079
just bought a gemstone necklace,

194
00:08:23,700 --> 00:08:26,279
and now she's showing it off
all over her social media every day.

195
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:28,480
So vain and tacky,

196
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,720
with such low-class manners.

197
00:08:30,439 --> 00:08:31,600
It's downright embarrassing.

198
00:08:32,160 --> 00:08:33,519
Mom, don't be upset.

199
00:08:33,839 --> 00:08:34,480
You're right.

200
00:08:35,439 --> 00:08:36,480
Right about what?

201
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:37,959
That gemstone necklace of hers

202
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:40,240
was a gift from the guy
who's pursuing Xiao Weiwei.

203
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:41,559
Just look at you.

204
00:08:42,279 --> 00:08:43,000
Mom,

205
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:45,960
don't forget who helped you
get that money back before.

206
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,480
Exactly.

207
00:08:47,879 --> 00:08:49,200
If it weren't for Chen,

208
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,120
our family would've...

209
00:08:50,919 --> 00:08:52,840
And you're calling him tacky?

210
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,759
That's not what I meant.

211
00:08:54,759 --> 00:08:55,759
It's okay, Mom.

212
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:56,519
It's fine.

213
00:08:57,759 --> 00:08:58,159
I...

214
00:08:58,600 --> 00:08:59,960
I'll get the door.

215
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:01,840
Coming!

216
00:09:04,159 --> 00:09:05,120
Miss Song!

217
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:07,440
May I ask if Mr. Ye Chen is home?

218
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:08,639
Yes.

219
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:09,720
Yes, he is.

220
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:10,480
Please, come in!

221
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:11,480
Come in,

222
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,279
No need to take off your shoes.

223
00:09:14,159 --> 00:09:15,799
Why did you bring gifts?

224
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:16,919
Please, come in.

225
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,000
Have a seat.

226
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:23,919
Who is it?

227
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:24,679
It's me.

228
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:26,559
Qin Aoxue.

229
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:27,759
Who are you looking for?

230
00:09:27,759 --> 00:09:28,799
I'm looking for my master.

231
00:09:28,919 --> 00:09:30,200
Master, I brought you gifts!

232
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:31,840
Master!

233
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:41,759
These are all for the two of us?

234
00:09:42,759 --> 00:09:44,320
Mr. Ye is a man of great stature,

235
00:09:44,639 --> 00:09:46,320
and his wife must be just as remarkable,

236
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:49,025
so I wouldn't dare offend you
with mere worldly gifts.

237
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:51,462
These are simply
small tokens for Mr. and Mrs. Xiao.

238
00:09:51,759 --> 00:09:52,759
Listen to that.

239
00:09:53,162 --> 00:09:54,600
So we're the greedy ones now?

240
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:57,279
If I've been presumptuous,

241
00:09:57,399 --> 00:09:58,279
please forgive me.

242
00:09:58,279 --> 00:09:58,960
No, no,

243
00:09:58,960 --> 00:09:59,559
not at all.

244
00:09:59,560 --> 00:10:00,790
How could that be presumptuous?

245
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:02,919
You really know how to read people.

246
00:10:03,070 --> 00:10:03,960
You understand us well.

247
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:04,919
You really get us.

248
00:10:04,919 --> 00:10:05,759
Mr. and Mrs. Xiao,

249
00:10:06,050 --> 00:10:07,360
I brought gifts for you as well.

250
00:10:08,039 --> 00:10:08,440
Look.

251
00:10:08,610 --> 00:10:10,120
A thousand-year-old Changbai ginseng.

252
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:10,960
N-Nice.

253
00:10:11,660 --> 00:10:13,600
And this,
a ten-thousand-year-old old tortoise.

254
00:10:15,279 --> 00:10:15,799
Nice.

255
00:10:17,190 --> 00:10:18,840
I don't bother with those flashy things.

256
00:10:20,879 --> 00:10:21,679
Master, Madam,

257
00:10:21,759 --> 00:10:22,919
I brought gifts for you too.

258
00:10:23,012 --> 00:10:24,235
Madam, try this.

259
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:25,675
Just one bite,

260
00:10:25,680 --> 00:10:27,490
and you'll go from 50-year-old
to 18-year-old.

261
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:29,600
These gifts are far too valuable.

262
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:30,990
- We can't accept...
- Wait, hold on.

263
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,679
Since when did we become your master
and madam?

264
00:10:32,679 --> 00:10:34,710
You're highly skilled in martial arts,
and you cured my poison.

265
00:10:34,725 --> 00:10:36,039
I already consider you my master.

266
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:37,440
Since when?

267
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:38,399
Just last night.

268
00:10:38,399 --> 00:10:39,720
I decided right before going to bed.

269
00:10:39,759 --> 00:10:40,887
Master, you don't know,

270
00:10:41,175 --> 00:10:42,850
after making that decision,

271
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:44,320
I slept so well!

272
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:47,360
Miss Qin, your little self-appointed act

273
00:10:47,590 --> 00:10:48,799
is actually quite adorable.

274
00:10:50,879 --> 00:10:51,399
Really?

275
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,120
Thanks.

276
00:10:53,500 --> 00:10:54,759
I was still mad at you just now.

277
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,150
Don't take it to heart.

278
00:10:58,879 --> 00:10:59,480
Mr. Ye,

279
00:10:59,919 --> 00:11:01,919
actually, the reason I came today
is to invite you

280
00:11:02,159 --> 00:11:03,080
to join the Song family

281
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:05,025
as our Chief Antique Appraiser.

282
00:11:08,390 --> 00:11:09,399
What do you mean by that?

283
00:11:09,662 --> 00:11:11,320
I just thought you were a good person,

284
00:11:11,320 --> 00:11:12,990
and now you're trying
to steal my master?

285
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:15,759
Working for the Song family
and being your master

286
00:11:15,759 --> 00:11:16,840
don't seem to conflict.

287
00:11:17,020 --> 00:11:18,120
How is that not a conflict?

288
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:20,800
If he works for you every day,
how's he supposed to teach me?

289
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:21,639
I don't care!

290
00:11:22,039 --> 00:11:22,600
Master,

291
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,519
you must also come to our Qin family.

292
00:11:24,519 --> 00:11:25,759
You can be our...

293
00:11:27,279 --> 00:11:28,600
Chief Medical Consultant.

294
00:11:29,360 --> 00:11:31,519
Shouldn't you discuss this
with Mr. Qin first?

295
00:11:31,639 --> 00:11:33,440
You can make the decisions directly?

296
00:11:35,187 --> 00:11:36,362
What, you think I'm like you?

297
00:11:36,370 --> 00:11:37,990
In my family,
everything goes through me.

298
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:39,320
Mr. Ye,

299
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:41,480
if you accept our offer,

300
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:42,840
you can name your terms.

301
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:44,279
Master, just say how much you want.

302
00:11:44,279 --> 00:11:45,290
My family will pay double.

303
00:11:49,279 --> 00:11:50,039
Besides money,

304
00:11:50,637 --> 00:11:53,295
I'm sure there are things
Mr. Ye values even more.

305
00:11:59,159 --> 00:11:59,679
Honey,

306
00:12:01,879 --> 00:12:03,559
Assistant to the Chairman of Xiao Group.

307
00:12:03,700 --> 00:12:04,879
Monthly salary will be 5,000.

308
00:12:04,879 --> 00:12:05,879
Full social insurance.

309
00:12:05,879 --> 00:12:06,870
Two days off every week.

310
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:07,480
Deal or not?

311
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:10,519
You called me honey?

312
00:12:11,660 --> 00:12:12,780
What else should I call you?

313
00:12:13,237 --> 00:12:14,360
Say it again.

314
00:12:17,525 --> 00:12:18,317
Honey.

315
00:12:42,825 --> 00:12:45,313
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

316
00:12:45,400 --> 00:12:49,153
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

317
00:12:49,613 --> 00:12:54,550
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

318
00:12:54,713 --> 00:12:57,000
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

319
00:12:57,313 --> 00:12:59,993
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

320
00:13:01,063 --> 00:13:03,688
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

321
00:13:03,988 --> 00:13:07,000
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

322
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:10,250
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

323
00:13:10,363 --> 00:13:13,325
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

324
00:13:13,593 --> 00:13:16,750
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

325
00:13:16,975 --> 00:13:20,725
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

326
00:13:20,725 --> 00:13:23,588
♪I belong to no one♪

327
00:13:23,650 --> 00:13:27,100
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

328
00:13:27,100 --> 00:13:29,775
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

329
00:13:29,775 --> 00:13:36,113
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪
